# 📝 To-Do App (React Native + Expo + Firebase)

This is a simple and beautiful **To-Do List App** built with **React Native** using **Expo** and integrated with **Google Sign-In** via **Firebase Authentication**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Google Sign-In using Firebase Authentication
- ✅ Create, view, and manage to-do tasks
- ✅ Clean and responsive UI
- ✅ Cross-platform (Android, iOS, and Web via Expo)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **React Native (Expo)**
- **Firebase Authentication**
- **React Navigation**
- **AsyncStorage** (for storing to-dos locally)

---

## 🔧 Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/to-do-app.git
cd to-do-app
